  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of ALSA Firmware</title>

    <para>The <application>ALSA Firmware</application> package
    is only needed by those with advanced requirements for their sound card.</para>

    <para>Install <application>ALSA Firmware</application> by
    running the following commands:</para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

